Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.59,0:04:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,花可不能吃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.26,0:04:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,燐 有很多花是可以吃的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.68,0:04:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}我家院子裡到了春天有很多好吃的花…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.64,0:04:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,連杜山同學都…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.69,0:04:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你們給我適可而止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.31,0:05:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,志摩負責禮物 包括調查週日前準備好！！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.57,0:05:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.36,0:05:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,奧村負責做蛋糕 不准買 自己做！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.07,0:05:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,好 雖然沒做過糕點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.53,0:05:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,子貓丸負責做採購 以及指導奧村
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.46,0:05:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,杜山和我一起裝飾房間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.00,0:05:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不愧是小坊 辦事能力真不簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.00,0:05:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,那個 小坊 我還是負責別的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.22,0:05:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,沒問題 你對日式糕點的熱情我很清楚 好好發揮它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.47,0:05:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不要隨便把蛋糕歸為日式糕點…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.89,0:05:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你的話肯定行！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.81,0:05:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,一起努力吧 子貓丸！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.77,0:05:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.65,0:05:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,聽好了 準備的時候被發現的話就沒意義了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.32,0:05:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,一定要萬分小心 那麼祝大家順利！！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.62,0:05:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,生日嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.97,0:06:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,志摩同學 來我們班幹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.55,0:06:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,那個 樸同學在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.85,0:06:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,回來了 樸——
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.77,0:06:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs63}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.98,0:06:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs63}是啊 是啊 這之後可…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.28,0:06:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.49,0:06:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,稍微談下好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.78,0:06:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,能過來嗎 這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.78,0:06:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那兩個人 莫非…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.42,0:06:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 突然說這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.08,0:06:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,太開心了 不愧是樸同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.55,0:06:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,無論是臉蛋還是性格都這麼贊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.18,0:06:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 奧村同學 能讀下原料單嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.51,0:06:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.06,0:07:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,四個雞蛋 400克砂糖 小麥…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.23,0:07:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.52,0:07:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,之後的就拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.32,0:07:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.20,0:07:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,沒…沒事 先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.96,0:07:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,大概這樣就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.79,0:07:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.25,0:07:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,勝呂同學好擅長剪紙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.84,0:07:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,算是吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.05,0:07:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,那…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.26,0:07:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.97,0:07:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,這個 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.52,0:07:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,跟…跟你沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.85,0:07:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,等下 勝呂同學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.15,0:07:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.58,0:08:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你跟他在交往嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.92,0:08:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,午休時很開心的在聊天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.59,0:08:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,志摩同學？ 沒有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.67,0:08:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.01,0:08:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,真的啦 那只是生…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.43,0:08:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Tan？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.72,0:08:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,他問了我一些關於丹頂鶴的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.14,0:08:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,那樣就好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.94,0:08:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,那種輕浮的人 絕對不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.57,0:08:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,在做什麼 燐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.65,0:08:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,生日蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.45,0:08:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,蛋糕？ 蛋糕是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.83,0:08:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,看了就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.37,0:08:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}發生了那種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.42,0:08:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}現在和奧村同學獨處 真有點尷尬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.84,0:08:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,接下來是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.10,0:09:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…用沙漏把粉均勻地撒上去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.68,0:09:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.85,0:09:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,子貓丸 很熟練嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.48,0:09:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,真沒做過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.27,0:09:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,看的多自然就會了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.36,0:09:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,奧村同學才真不像第一次做糕點呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.57,0:09:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,真的很擅長料理啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.87,0:09:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,還好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.07,0:09:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我們家全是光棍 大家做料理都超爛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.45,0:09:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,只能自己做了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.75,0:09:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.42,0:09:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,但是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.21,0:09:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不為自己 為別人做料理真的很開心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.05,0:09:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.22,0:09:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 做出最棒的蛋糕吧 子貓丸！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.31,0:09:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,糟了 海綿蛋糕最關鍵要吸入空氣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.44,0:09:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,輕一點 慢一點！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.40,0:09:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,別停啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.77,0:09:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.66,0:09:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,真有幹勁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.41,0:10:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,小雪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.95,0:10:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,今天早上收到通知 訂購的藥草到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.37,0:10:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.75,0:10:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,那個 正十字學院 惡魔藥學科…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.75,0:10:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,這次是我個人訂購的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.59,0:10:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,這可真稀奇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.51,0:10:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.72,0:10:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我聽說了party的事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.14,0:10:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,是詩惠美的想法吧 神木同學肯定會開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.35,0:10:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,一半是為了自己
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.15,0:10:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽和婆婆給我慶祝過生日 但沒跟朋友在一起慶祝過
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.28,0:10:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,現在能夠這樣上補習班 還結識了朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.49,0:10:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我覺得現在大家能一起過個party吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.92,0:10:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,有點自作主張了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.17,0:10:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我覺得很棒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.34,0:10:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,說起來 燐和小雪的生日是哪天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.01,0:11:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,12月27日
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.47,0:11:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,辦過生日party嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.35,0:11:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,辦過哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.14,0:11:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,勉強吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.26,0:11:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,勉強？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.39,0:11:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,因為生日臨近聖誕節
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.90,0:11:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,修道院的大家一直都在聖誕節時給我們慶祝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.28,0:11:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,但看來我還是完全不瞭解生日
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.99,0:11:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,希望Party順利
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.21,0:11:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,小雪也會參加吧 肯定很愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.98,0:11:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,這個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.18,0:11:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,還只是樣品
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.07,0:11:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,嘛 交給我就是這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.69,0:11:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,不對！ 不對！ 不對！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.65,0:11:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,哪裡不對了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.78,0:12:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,完全不對嘛 怎麼回事 子貓丸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.45,0:12:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是盯著他的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.32,0:12:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我一下沒注意就…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.33,0:12:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,別欺負子貓丸 這哪裡有問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.86,0:12:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不是很完美嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.32,0:12:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,做錯啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.58,0:12:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,大家怎麼了 我覺得是很棒的生日蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.22,0:12:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,生日蛋糕跟聖誕蛋糕是不同的東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.43,0:12:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我們活到15歲才知道真相啊 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.60,0:12:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,這個怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.15,0:12:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,一直以來非常感謝 小小的心意 ——補習班全體成員
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.24,0:12:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,為了慶祝上帝誕生的蛋糕 居然送給我這個惡魔？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.87,0:12:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow Fantastic!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.09,0:12:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.34,0:13:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀 便裝也很可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.05,0:13:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.18,0:13:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.73,0:13:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,都那樣忠告過了 樸真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.50,0:13:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.50,0:13:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.00,0:13:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,志摩真奇怪～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.80,0:13:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,這個如何
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.34,0:13:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不錯哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.88,0:13:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,喂喂 靠的太近了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.77,0:14:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,小雲好像在收集這個系列
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.32,0:14:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,眼睛圓溜溜 好可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.24,0:14:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好可愛 好可愛…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.53,0:14:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好可愛？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.20,0:14:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我也很喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.08,0:14:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}喜歡… 喜歡…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.17,0:14:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,喜歡？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.25,0:14:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,難道是兩廂情願？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.17,0:14:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不會吧 再怎麼說進展也太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.97,0:14:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.27,0:14:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.15,0:14:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,糟了 我沒帶傘
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.07,0:14:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係 我帶了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.49,0:14:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,居然同打一把傘！！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.54,0:14:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.58,0:15:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,灰塵進眼睛了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.83,0:15:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,哪只眼睛？ 讓我看下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.18,0:15:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,住手！！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.11,0:15:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.82,0:15:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,小雲？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.90,0:15:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你們在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.07,0:15:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,被發現了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.95,0:15:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼被發現了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.91,0:15:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你也是的 居然在這裡跟樸Ki…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.37,0:15:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,想跟她Kiss…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.63,0:15:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.75,0:15:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,說什麼啊 小雲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.84,0:15:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,那是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.38,0:15:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,兩個人鬼鬼祟祟的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.97,0:15:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,這是為了小雲的生日禮物…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.89,0:16:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,就是這麼回事 所以暴露了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.73,0:16:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你是笨蛋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.27,0:16:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.31,0:16:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼生氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.86,0:16:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,只為難我一個人 絕對不原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.74,0:16:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼叫為難你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.87,0:16:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不對嗎 大家只是想利用我熱鬧一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.87,0:16:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,小雲 現在應該坦誠心扉 好好高興一下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.50,0:16:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起 是我不好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.46,0:16:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,是我說要舉辦生日Party的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.67,0:16:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,根本不用道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.63,0:16:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,杜山同學為了讓你高興很努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.84,0:16:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,大家給你慶生對你有那麼麻煩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.39,0:16:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,不是這個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.52,0:16:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.48,0:16:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我是說不公平啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.06,0:16:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不公平？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.69,0:16:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,這種時候突然辦生日party多不公平啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.53,0:16:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,開學到現在錯過生日的人該怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.78,0:17:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定有人已經到16歲了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.62,0:17:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,之前你們不是聊過摩托車駕照什麼的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.79,0:17:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,不愧是小雲 真敏銳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.84,0:17:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,果然沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.50,0:17:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,大家的生日也一起慶祝吧 否則我可不認同
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.68,0:17:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.22,0:17:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼… 小坊 志摩和神木同學的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.85,0:17:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,還有樸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.10,0:17:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼要準備四份禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.15,0:17:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,另外之前勝呂和志摩交的錢要還回去 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.69,0:17:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼嘛 真麻煩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.07,0:17:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼 加上將要過生日的我們一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.78,0:17:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,大家一起 慶祝大家的生日吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.92,0:17:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,平假名可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.59,0:17:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 我來教你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.60,0:18:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,H—A—P—P—Y
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.85,0:18:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.35,0:18:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs49.5\shad0\bord3\pos(960,460.5)\3c&H3F3F49&\c&HEFEFFA&}生日快樂 補習班的大家！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.90,0:18:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那邊還要飲料嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.61,0:18:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,完成了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.07,0:18:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,喲 等好久了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.15,0:18:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,這是奧村同學做的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.28,0:18:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀 這是我唯一具有生產性的特長嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.03,0:18:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,自己說出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.76,0:18:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,子貓丸！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.86,0:18:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,子貓丸 謝謝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.16,0:19:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,1—2—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.62,0:19:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,生日快樂！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.17,0:19:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼 大家久等了 開始交換禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.43,0:19:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,能得到什麼禮物 大家請期待抽籤的結果吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.30,0:19:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我先來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.40,0:19:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了 小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.44,0:19:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,沒什麼 覺得大家都很開心的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.07,0:19:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,小雪不開心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.24,0:19:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,很開心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.12,0:19:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,最近一直很奇怪啊 小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.75,0:19:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,別人告訴我們生日是12月27日
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.13,0:19:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,但其實沒什麼感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.71,0:20:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我們不知道自己是誰的孩子 何時何地出生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.72,0:20:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.81,0:20:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 我們的母親到底是什麼樣的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.10,0:20:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我是在橋下撿到你們的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.27,0:20:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}又來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.98,0:20:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}才不是騙你呢 明明是冬天 有這麼大的西瓜飄過來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.61,0:20:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}切開來 你們就在裡面了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.74,0:20:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.91,0:20:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那時在橫切還是豎切西瓜的問題上 還發生了不小的爭執呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.03,0:20:29.24,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\3c&H776C7C&\fad(300,300)}In the middle of night(And you follow the light)
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.54,0:20:31.58,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\3c&H776C7C&\fad(300,300)}I was far from the light
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.91,0:20:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是切得不好 不光是西瓜 你們也會被切成兩半的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.25,0:20:36.42,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\3c&H776C7C&\fad(300,300)}They freely pass me by
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.42,0:20:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}才不是那樣的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.92,0:20:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,父親插科打諢 沒告訴我們實情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.46,0:20:42.67,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\3c&H776C7C&\fad(300,300)}Then I'm totally out of space and seeking my friends
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.88,0:20:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,但只有那次…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.88,0:20:46.76,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\3c&H776C7C&\fad(300,300)}Is there anyone who needs me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.47,0:20:50.81,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\3c&H776C7C&\fad(300,300)}I hear what you say
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.10,0:20:53.52,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\3c&H776C7C&\fad(300,300)}There's the tiniest hope
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.39,0:20:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}第一次見到你們的時候也是這樣的雪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.81,0:20:56.23,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,45)\blur2\3c&H776C7C&\fad(300,300)}You can change yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.98,0:20:58.31,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,45)\blur2\3c&H776C7C&\fad(300,300)}If you want to
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.77,0:21:01.57,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\3c&H776C7C&\fad(300,300)}Then you find the door
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.90,0:21:04.32,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\3c&H776C7C&\fad(300,300)}We can walk from the past
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.03,0:21:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,最後也只有那一點線索
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.11,0:21:08.58,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\3c&H776C7C&\fad(300,300)}I was a frog in a wall
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.61,0:21:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,到現在我們已經無法知道真正的生日是哪天了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.99,0:21:11.62,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\3c&H776C7C&\fad(300,300)}Smile like you've never done
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.49,0:21:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,真的？ 太好玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.79,0:21:14.12,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\3c&H776C7C&\fad(300,300)}I'm so fine
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.96,0:21:19.75,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\3c&H776C7C&\fad(300,300)}Then you hold me tight under bad weather
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.62,0:21:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.54,0:21:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,祝賀你的誕生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.34,0:21:22.63,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,45)\blur2\3c&H776C7C&\fad(300,300)}If you uderstand why
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.80,0:21:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,不管是哪天 我都為小雪的出生感到高興
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.37,0:21:26.72,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,45)\blur2\3c&H776C7C&\fad(300,300)}I was crying on the river so
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.72,0:21:28.30,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\3c&H776C7C&\fad(300,300)}Dwell on my self
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.47,0:21:31.76,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\3c&H776C7C&\fad(300,300)}All the time
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.05,0:21:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.10,0:21:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,那邊的兩位
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.06,0:21:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,2號和7號 你們分別選哪個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.73,0:21:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧
